scenes.description: Amelia Watson showcases the details of her new 3D model, focusing on her shoes, leggings, and accessories like her watch and stethoscope.
Amelia celebrates her official 3D debut with high-energy poses and begins a tour of her detective office.
Amelia introduces her dog Bubba and shows off his 'tricks,' including flying, doing a flip, and dancing.
Amelia presents a conspiracy board featuring an 'evil' version of herself, asking Bubba to attack it.
Amelia shows off her empty fish tank, joking that Bubba ate all the fish.
Amelia explores the office window and tries to reach some decorative hanging stars.
Amelia shows her workstation monitors, claiming she uses them to look at her stream chat.
Amelia points out 'evil' versions of the other Hololive Myth members on another board and explains the Japanese word 'hako' (box).
Amelia receives a phone call from Hololive CEO Yagoo, who assigns her a new mysterious case at a crime scene.
